{"tid":796593,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"政治篇：想跟特首說聲加油🤟🏻🤟🏻","createTime":"2018-08-28T01:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T03:16:39.000Z","uid":69810,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fc77c9ba59c63ebcab941b9b4da01616e73ffe8d","tid":796593,"uid":69810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:16:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得現在社會真的充滿怨氣，但不只年輕人才不滿現況。自從有網絡的出現，加上社會愈來愈自由，經常有反獌page和球迷討論區，大家多了表達不滿的途徑。我相對處於一個比較體諒的角色，因為就算有多少不滿也好，你一定要 be honest 的是，你在這個球會一定得到某些benefit，不是每樣事情你都覺得「唔gur」（很不爽）。有時打開報紙，見到有人好激烈地反對某些事，或者從早到晚叫摩佬下台，我反而覺得：「嘩！使唔使呀？」<br />\n<br />\n你問我摩佬可以怎樣幫助曼聯？我又不是 expert，如果我是 expert，我做了摩佬啦！我覺得好多人指教摩佬可以怎樣怎樣做，而我在做歌手這幾年間，亦有好多人 challenge 我的作品或者決定，問我為何不這樣做呀？其實我有九百幾個理由，但是觀眾不會知道你背後 concern 過的東西，亦看不見你面對的制肘。有時我無法告訴你為何不這樣做，但我有我的原因，摩佬可能都是一樣。<br />\n<br />\n我想跟摩連奴說句「加油」呀！他的壓力必然好大。先不要考慮他做每一個決定背後的原因，不要去 judge 他做得好不好，我真是好想跟他說一聲「加油」，因為這個角色實在很難做。我不想再對他施加壓力，想給他一份鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n我不覺得一個領隊、或者一個球會可以怎樣幫助球迷，一個領隊應該盡最大能力去提高球會的成績，但哪個人可以幫到獌聯呢？就是你摩佬！重點不是要求球會給你多少成績和福利，而是在有多少錢和福利的情況下，適當地調整個人心態。分數可能是愈多愈好，但 at the end 都是在乎你怎樣面對，所以我好希望自己的音樂，可以為觀眾帶來一些魔性和鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS1AMNHaeSSaZZtx7EAoAUp4ZGXVRVPCnTu8cxmMQYqErY7-EhoNg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcS1AMNHaeSSaZZtx7EAoAUp4ZGXVRVPCnTu8cxmMQYqErY7-EhoNg&h=be3c2b71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bea9160fbc274d75fbea6dff1bcf70211934006","tid":796593,"uid":69810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/091720_6ab4575eedfa50bdd80c11115ac27462.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F091720_6ab4575eedfa50bdd80c11115ac27462.png&h=6429551f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1270908eedbb91d23bf7d5874dad257f43e69dcd","tid":796593,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48404d307818934b1f4a1f9341f6d49b9088213e","tid":796593,"uid":69810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1270908eedbb91d23bf7d5874dad257f43e69dcd","tid":796593,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b74cf5d2074394913aa9057f4299c94b3973394","tid":796593,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:30:39.000Z","msg":"Daddy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0063da02006e790a73c04b13486c1987692eb4b1","tid":796593,"uid":69810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b74cf5d2074394913aa9057f4299c94b3973394","tid":796593,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:30:39.000Z","msg":"Daddy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:32:07.000Z","msg":"是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984b04bc5a6ecda699379657236ce6db9df50440","tid":796593,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:16:39.000Z","msg":"加油呀摩子"}]}